{"tid":1541983,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"[圖文教學]覺得自己英文唔好但想加入twitter文宣戰線","createTime":"2019-09-04T17:13:23.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-22T14:11:45.000Z","uid":106648,"like":51,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":31,"replies":[{"pid":"e5eb07d023ed831519baa7e69c793b5fb1a5fe08","tid":1541983,"uid":106648,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T17:13:23.000Z","msg":"第一次開post好害羞！<br />\n希望可以幫到想試吓twitter文宣戰嘅手足，<br />\n自問都係新手，只能出個非常簡單嘅圖文教學，<br />\n等英文唔好但又想幫手嘅巴絲一齊衝出國際！<br />\n喺教學之前請容許我帶個頭盔，我教嘅係基本技巧，<br />\n至於點樣先至可以達到最佳嘅宣傳效果，例如點上trending啊、analytics啊，我係未鑽研到咁深嘅。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">廢話可skip 重點睇呢度</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: large;\">1. 開account</span> </strong><br />\n唔特別教啦，各位攞返當初你哋開任何一個social media嘅基本知識就得。Icon啊自介啊記住有，如果唔係就會好似五毛嗰啲fake account咁。<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: large;\">2. follow同道中人</span> </strong><br />\nsearch #followbackhongkong<br />\n目的係攞文宣素材，咁樣即使英文唔好都可以輕鬆retweet。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/hUCR9g6.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FhUCR9g6.png&h=0b6bb73b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: large;\">3. follow外國人</span> </strong><br />\n去名人account(e.g. 侵侵、Uffee Elbaek、Lady Gaga)搵你嘅target。呢步好重要，你要一個宣傳去到國際，就一定要令你target customer睇到你嘅嘢。你要做嘅就係鳩follow外國人，等佢哋follow返你，咁樣佢先會睇到你嘅tweets。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: large;\">4. 萬事俱備，可以開始retweet了</span></strong><br />\n搵個你啱feel嘅tweet<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ZQ5wpRv.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FZQ5wpRv.png&h=9242312f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/21xZyLj.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F21xZyLj.png&h=73f298ed&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\nretweet完成！<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: large;\">5. 進階版，retweet with comments</span></strong><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ddvz64D.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fddvz64D.png&h=1f058de9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\">5.1 可以加入啱用嘅tags</span><br />\n基本類: #AntiELAB  #HongKongProtests  #NoExtraditionToChina<br />\n警暴類: #PoliceBrutality <br />\n支那類: #BoycottChina #ChiNazi <br />\n國際類 #StandWithHongKong #FreeHongKong <br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\">5.2 除hashtag外不妨練習吓英文，加啲感想</span><br />\n畢竟練習帶來進步，唔好俾所謂嘅英文唔好框死咗你，practice makes perfect!<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><strong>6. 更進階版，個人製作文宣</strong></span><br />\n去到呢步，我已經無嘢教到你，歡迎加入tg group一齊製作文宣，使用已翻譯文宣兼討論戰術。<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><a href=\"http://t.me/twitter4HK\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Ftwitter4HK&d=aWTYmjKPTw65bzRUwiqYJGzUwbN2nhMFbUYjFdDHJd4%3D&h=7b35f952\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">t.me/twitter4HK</a></span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\">記住幾點</span><br />\n1.twitter係計retweet數，你禁爆個心心係幫唔到個post<br />\n<br />\n2.同樣地，因為twitter係計retweet數，所以最好唔好只係tweet人地嘅retweet。禁埋入原post，集中推高原post嘅retweet數。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/CgNOr54.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FCgNOr54.png&h=6d04b692&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n3.得閒post吓自己嘢，如果唔係會俾人當bot封account。用吓中文都無問題。<br />\n<br />\n4.唔好因為英文而卻步，因為你只需要禁個retweet已經有推廣作用，各位加油！<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\">光復香港 時代革命</span></span></strong>"},{"pid":"e0401a97ca5b555d10876fb1ca667d7b087e0e8e","tid":1541983,"uid":117906,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T17:14:34.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">撤LLM 對準政權</span></strong></span><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/3E7OjKb.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F3E7OjKb.gif&h=66b4ea40&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/zNutjAi.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FzNutjAi.jpg&h=1817afe5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: orange;\">得到黨媒認證</span></strong></span><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/sELTeyX.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FsELTeyX.png&h=0e8c0efe&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">#Chinazi旗係一個符號，不斷向世界輸出反共思想！</span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\">#Chinazi 赤納粹</span></span></strong><br />\nChinazi就係China+Nazi。<br />\n赤=共產紅色恐怖, 納粹不解釋。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\"> 全民反共 對準政權！</span></span></strong><br />\n黑警、黨鐵，港共全部都係人民既敵人<br />\n而背後一直有一個終極大Boss中共<br />\n<br />\n呢一刻中共絕對係十個煲得兩個蓋，準備爆煲。<br />\n今日唔號召世界圍堵中共，更待何時？<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\">用#Chinazi黎connect全世界</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: orange;\">1. Connect所有黃絲。</span></strong><br />\n殘酷既現實係，並唔係所有黃絲都支持勇武。但黃絲最驚就係共產黨打到黎，一於用反共connect呢班淺黃!<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: orange;\">2. Connect部分中立/藍絲。</span></strong><br />\n中立/藍絲既上一輩，全部都係親身經歷過六四既年代，唔少甚至係大陸生活過。係大陸生活上所面對既不公義、中共點砌人生豬肉、佢地可能比我地感受更深。佢地唔會否認對共產黨既恐懼！一齊黎喚醒佢地對中共既不信任！<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: orange;\">3. Connect全世界</span></strong><br />\nNazi既惡行到今時今日都依然係全世界既傷口，但佢地未必注意到係21世紀有個同Nazi不遑多讓既Chinazi！用#chinazi旗加海量文宣，話比佢地知我地既共同敵人係中共！<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>目標：全香港市民都知到呢個符號！<br />\n請大家用各種創意方法令大家知道呢道Chinazi旗！<br />\n記住！存在即勝利！</span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: orange;\">雙手奉上</span></strong><br />\n<img src=\"https://upload.cc/i1/2019/09/02/9dojRG.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.cc%2Fi1%2F2019%2F09%2F02%2F9dojRG.png&h=baf47345&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/JXMrzU3.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FJXMrzU3.jpg&h=4fd76574&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/uZFWW8o.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FuZFWW8o.jpg&h=4196affc&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"651438c0ffcdf3073f70295813442501ae6d35c6","tid":1541983,"uid":106648,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T17:16:57.000Z","msg":"自推一下，整到好眼訓<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/zzz.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n訓嚕！<br />\n大家加油！"},{"pid":"4d7f3d3d6e1cf3e475911309a441a78172af5801","tid":1541983,"uid":106648,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T17:18:41.000Z","msg":"2"},{"pid":"d68fc574d21682e4e1b5690733fdfef43dae46f3","tid":1541983,"uid":106648,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T17:19:40.000Z","msg":"3"},{"pid":"bfa7520a7c92d6a4ab7b21676c66c83effbd1f8e","tid":1541983,"uid":300295,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T17:23:57.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"aa0136113478a166548e9e497508d65c6a3e2b83","tid":1541983,"uid":205919,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T17:25:02.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"ddff8b65d9f5ff7ad42e3bb2c1aa0eb1323c393d","tid":1541983,"uid":210254,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T17:27:29.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"0dc76c7c2b949825f84b811f415b3743149296d4","tid":1541983,"uid":129760,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T17:32:54.000Z","msg":"仲可以申請嚟推呢個投票<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://twitter.com/hongkonghermit/status/1169216501502468097?s=12\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fhongkonghermit%2Fstatus%2F1169216501502468097%3Fs%3D12&d=aWTYmjKPTw65bzRUwiqYJGzUwbN2nhMFbUYjFdDHJd4%3D&h=345e2e5e\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fhongkonghermit%2Fstatus%2F1169216501502468097%3Fs%3D12&h=31ff0d87\" target=\"_blank\">https://twitter.com/hongkonghermit/status/1169216501502468097?s=12</a>"},{"pid":"e9786c0b49cb70459b44a818b9b386a8a8ca1cc2","tid":1541983,"uid":129760,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T17:33:31.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">光復香港<br />\n時代革命</span></span>"},{"pid":"4e3231e2b204fec19af126e4cacf4c4c592947f6","tid":1541983,"uid":86869,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T18:07:14.000Z","msg":"Follow左68人就話我到左上限點算"},{"pid":"d3ed6b0f7760d4ee549ae1a75b2dd8a4e75d51d7","tid":1541983,"uid":106648,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"4e3231e2b204fec19af126e4cacf4c4c592947f6","tid":1541983,"uid":86869,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T18:07:14.000Z","msg":"Follow左68人就話我到左上限點算"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T22:57:54.000Z","msg":"出吓post先<br />\nretweet吓，又post吓自己嘢，唔好心急<br />\n佢當你係bot，過一排會解封"},{"pid":"20d7d24b9b8faec898d9a6d82002d5c78d8b34fc","tid":1541983,"uid":106648,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T23:07:59.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"b27ad50de98ab3aa3629c6ef1623deab74bad191","tid":1541983,"uid":106648,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T23:45:11.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"d885517222cec4c04f42dfa552a67020efeb6041","tid":1541983,"uid":105797,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T23:51:39.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d067263fbcd384e9e590ceb0431b0f10fbf254c9","tid":1541983,"uid":105797,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T23:52:24.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9b191886704ae00da7d821aa0c8a41d5333a7bc0","tid":1541983,"u