Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c9940622a868d00db8921c5e05a2b3960337d749","tid":1541983,"uid":181035,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-05T02:20:08.000Z","msg":"記得set好啲私隱野 唔好show email同電話"},{"pid":"30ef5731825189ad27df84b1132a2c27a07f896c","tid":1541983,"uid":105797,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-05T02:35:29.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0f7156e3b9e14f9508fc6e99734ef6d2dee9e869","tid":1541983,"uid":124507,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-05T02:42:58.000Z","msg":"齊齊練英文"},{"pid":"1c19acebe7a64349061260bf3332091a79def96e","tid":1541983,"uid":105797,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-05T05:46:35.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"0a10494e604b964f22511e8fa1355fcc785440a6","tid":1541983,"uid":89011,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-05T06:17:51.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"33f3efaf41949cd9f881f76e21c5f594565f1507","tid":1541983,"uid":3149,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-05T06:37:02.000Z","msg":"Push <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"143b4ed62de2f1380c92c85ae7c79f78d222fcf8","tid":1541983,"uid":20137,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-05T06:56:01.000Z","msg":"開左個新ac隔左陣要電話認證 twitter 安唔安全?"},{"pid":"c61d7978efbf755017e52aaddfee317e6dd6762c","tid":1541983,"uid":106648,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"143b4ed62de2f1380c92c85ae7c79f78d222fcf8","tid":1541983,"uid":20137,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-05T06:56:01.000Z","msg":"開左個新ac隔左陣要電話認證 twitter 安唔安全?"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-05T09:38:06.000Z","msg":"twitter係要的，<br />\n可以認證咗先，<br />\n之後可以del返，我都係咁做。"},{"pid":"f7476ed8e769bed185c5fb776c8238d0e8388fbf","tid":1541983,"uid":106648,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-05T09:42:56.000Z","msg":"Twitter 攻略<br />\n[#使用方法]<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">1. 帳號經電話確認後可刪掉電話號碼，但帳號依然可用<br />\n2. 一個手機號可開10個帳號，但不能連續開<br />\n3. 用電郵開既帳號，很快會話帳號問題，要加手機確認，這是Twitter防5毛開帳號，正常現像。</span></span></strong><br />\n4. Twitter有rate limit。 約一分鐘一個tweet或retweet。太快會被暫停一會<br />\n5. 公開自己Twitter, 唔好set private mode<br />\n6. 要個人化自己個twitter，唔好淨係政治，tweet吓食嘜野，追下星，like吓貓貓狗狗，證明自己唔係bot。用英文<br />\n7. 關事先好hashtag，例如女仔受到性暴力先好hashtag #feminist @emmawatson。唔好警察擲tear gas又tag女權<br />\n8. 開新tweet盡量少tag人<br />\n9. Hashtag儘量集中喺1，2個, 太多會當spam<br />\n10. 新開帳號一般需要2日左右別人才會搜尋到你的tweet<br />\n11. 搜尋關鍵字無論有冇#都一樣可以搜到<br />\n[#基本操作]<br />\n12. 見到同路人就互follow, like, retweet, comment，咁先冇咁易死帳。<br />\n13. 見到三毛唔好覆(只會boost popularity),鬼佬淨係睇正文唔睇留言，佢見咁多人tweet就當係真，所以唔好覆<br />\n14. 人地用英文tweet就英文覆，日本tweet就日文覆，免令人反感<br />\n15. 大家有共識set好時間一齊trend(hashtag+圖+互retweet,推上熱門)<br />\n16. 最好就是開新Tweet, 回覆都可以不過要有關鍵字才可給人搜到。Retweet及like別人搜尋是看不到的<br />\n17. 納粹係雙面刀，係好多人嘅創傷，唔好亂用，用都要解釋清楚。<br />\n18. 美國同香港時差12小時以上，香港組頂唔住眼瞓就交比外國撚。大家要呼籲l外國朋友/住外國嘅香港人入曬嚟推tweet<br />\n19. 少抄人地野，回覆多用自己感想免似5毛<br />\n-&mdash;<br />\n海量文宣在此 @hkstandstrong_promo_int<br />\n暫時咁多，有其他意見，歡迎提出<br />\n----<br />\n三有二無<br />\n見自己人post/hashtag就:<br />\n1.like 2.comment 3.retweet <br />\n有支狗Comment假消息:<br />\n1.ignore佢,等佢發癲 2.report佢<br />\n---<br />\n注意。Twitter 同一電話可開10個帳號。但要慢慢開。連開最多5個就唔俾再開。隔幾小時開一個可以。新帳號隔一陣多會顯示給屏蔽。要電話確認。確認後可刪走電話而帳號永遠可用。<br />\n少retweet. Retweet 別人 search不到的。<br />\n新帳號別人search 唔到你的內容。<br />\n一般要1至2日別人才可經搜尋才看到<br />\n---<br />\nCOPY自telegram文宣group"},{"pid":"54e39dcff130d7beb3e9a214545492651f504e0c","tid":1541983,"uid":106648,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-05T10:38:08.000Z","msg":"推 大家一齊做啦好嗎"},{"pid":"4ccf636232658fa06708fbee56faefeebb592791","tid":1541983,"uid":105797,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-05T13:59:56.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"1c70e7ab9f1fb10527c9e9789769cf8cd6ed5dcb","tid":1541983,"uid":105797,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-05T14:00:36.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"78c2e1a98920860630f84753395c84813b141521","tid":1541983,"uid":105797,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-05T15:04:37.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4a6538cd25b0940249fb3bc8c2bb739b10ba2fa3","tid":1541983,"uid":106648,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"78c2e1a98920860630f84753395c84813b141521","tid":1541983,"uid":105797,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-05T15:04:37.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-05T16:03:32.000Z","msg":"多謝你啊巴打<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"825e595a25b538943296f6e0d183726df1f4185d","tid":1541983,"uid":103470,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-05T16:06:18.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />